<p>I am feeling incredibly grateful for every lab member. Everyone pitched in to make the situation ever so more bearable for the others, showing kindness and support.</p>

<p>We finished our 2020 with a very special outdoor Christmas event visiting a small peninsula at Lake Bienne. It was a very good moment to share.</p>

<p>Thank you everyone!</p>

